news_header: Fresh product deliveries are normalizing after traffic issues and system defects affected availability.
news_text: Prismos and S-market manufacturing shelves have seen a rapid decline. Fresh toimivant's deliveries are returning to normal after significant traffic problems. Since last Friday, defects in the themion system have impacted the availability of fresh products. This led to a surge in demand for other manufacturing salads at S Group stores over the weekend. Fresh ylösvant identified the fault during the weekend, and deliveries are now back on track, with full normalization expected by the end of the week. Fresh pahoivant has apologized for the inconveniences caused.
